plot:
Helen, who is a priest, is approached by scientist Lisbeth with a 
desperate plea for help. A young man, who has been sent to a high 
security psychiatric ward after having killed an old couple, has 
attempted suicide while rambling about God. In a race against time the 
two women begin a shocking journey deeper and deeper into the sick mind 
of a young man's soul.                Fuente: IMDb
title: I lossens time
